官，她的奮鬥故事激勵人心。<br />\n<br />\n僅帶300美元到美國做清潔工<br />\n據美國哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）報道，現年41歲的Diana Trujillo來自哥倫比亞，父母在她12歲離異，她自此在單親家庭成長，直至17歲時決定獨自到美國，身上僅帶著300美元（約2,300港元）。當時她不懂英文，找了一份清潔工作，半工讀在佛羅里達大學（University of Florida）完成學業。<br />\n<br />\nDiana指早年的移民經歷，令她凡事盡力而為，不會輕言否定自己，尤其自己來自一個機會有限的國家，去到美國可說處處都是機遇。她一直都以積極的態度面對前路︰<br />\n&quot;我不會說，無法相信我要當清潔工或晚上工作，而是想著很高興我有一份工作，可以買食物，而且有房子讓我睡覺。過去每一刻都很重要，也造就今天的我。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n加入NASA向家人證明能力<br />\n她憶述在佛羅里達大學選科時，根本不知道自己想讀甚麼，但她被雜誌上的女太空人圖片吸引，於是確定路向主修航空航天工程，向太空夢進發。她更留意到航天業缺乏懂西班牙文的人才，而她具備這方面優勢。<br />\n<br />\n在大學四年級時，她申請了NASA Academy培訓計劃，成為第一位加入計劃的西班牙裔女性，並在2007年正式獲NASA聘請，現在是噴射推進實驗室的一員。她不諱言加入NASA的部分原因是，想向家人尤其是男性親友證明，女性也很有價值。<br />\n<br />\n兩孩之母身教凡事盡所能<br />\n當年17歲的少女現在已是兩孩之母，也是從事科學工作中為數不多的拉丁裔之一。Diana有感一路走來太不可思議，不時反問自己為何能走到這一步。當擔起「毅力號」指揮官時，她代表的不僅僅是自己。<br />\n&quot;我知道我不會一個人走，我做的每一件事都代表著國家，必須每次都盡我所能。&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2890000/2893469/NASA_thumb_20210305_E_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2890000%2F2893469%2FNASA_thumb_20210305_E_1024.jpg&h=39597b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2890000/2893469/09_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2890000%2F2893469%2F09_1024.jpg&h=90c43f7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T21:14:47.000Z","msg":"香港人要準備幾千萬先會走難........"},{"pid":"8d4c60ecfb5572bda3751d5e3a61e60312f26535","tid":2434871,"uid":90400,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T21:17:16.000Z","msg":"係美國好多無乜錢既大學生都會打2,3份pt維持生活"},{"pid":"c663afadc2f50760716e243266e1283f96db06ed","tid":2434871,"uid":375135,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T21:18:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diana_Trujillo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FDiana_Trujillo&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedTQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=045dbbd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diana_Trujillo</a><br />\n<br />\nUniversity of Florida - Aerospace Engineering<br />\n<br />\nUniversity of Maryland where she was part of the Professor Roberts' research team focused on robots in space operations.<br />\nIn 2007, she earned a Bachelor's degree in Aerospace Engineering from the University of Maryland<br />\n<br />\nHer story was turned into a children's science book titled &quot;Mars Science Lab - Engineer&quot; by Kari Cornell and Fatima Khan"},{"pid":"677239e89cd4aaf1218fd3a54aec4c306c4c970a","tid":2434871,"uid":130626,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"9ba5ffea30698afab85127eaca8a317f4459defa","tid":2434871,"uid":121546,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f379eb67267200fd3b74ddd467ff0e848016073e","tid":2434871,"uid":27251,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T20:56:28.000Z","msg":"真係好佩服呢啲人咁有毅力，唔知點樣不眠不休工作讀書，可以半工讀到咁既程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n證明左點解人地成功，我就失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T21:00:13.000Z","msg":"首先要有讀依一科既天份<br />\n然後仲要有咁既體力<br />\n最後就係要有毅力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T21:24:08.000Z","msg":"同埋本身佢既讀書基因都唔錯，佢阿媽後生嗰陣係醫科生，不過因為大左肚所以先至冇再讀落去"},{"pid":"0230ab97993394369a625704486736d5a6efdd05","tid":2434871,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"f379eb67267200fd3b74ddd467ff0e848016073e","tid":2434871,"uid":27251,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T20:56:28.000Z","msg":"真係好佩服呢啲人咁有毅力，唔知點樣不眠不休工作讀書，可以半工讀到咁既程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n證明左點解人地成功，我就失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T21:26:29.000Z","msg":"唔通同你講佢同professor性交易咩，梗係話半工讀啦"},{"pid":"f67728b289b5c5e5bc4d1af3c4fb5dc0cd1f776c","tid":2434871,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T21:27:16.000Z","msg":"美國夢"},{"pid":"691ba0303bc8336c30b0c3c233a68cdda7b839e4","tid":2434871,"uid":124372,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T21:28:08.000Z","msg":"呢個標題又係類似cnn手法<br />\n首先佢17歲美國唔識英文<br />\n但佢唔係無讀書<br />\n相反佢仲要數學,物理都攞A<br />\n至於清潔對於外國大學生做part-time好正常<br />\n我當年都係洗碗掃地take order一腳踢<br />\n係外國做厭惡性行業係好好paid<br />\n你估落後地方<br />\n但啲盲毛睇就以為條女係由文盲到現在係頂尖科學家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef5ebc34c547b66976d65905c9954636a0d5fc1","tid":2434871,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T22:56:59.000Z","msg":"佢唔識英文唔代表無讀過書呀⋯⋯？"},{"pid":"dacc5a7ef39829969fc9b13365ea686555099c7e","tid":2434871,"uid":23061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8264f7973bd1aeb07cf44481bd433de2cc768fc","tid":2434871,"uid":375135,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2bb14de245e8c23cefc312f39ecdd659eaa413f5","tid":2434871,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T20:26:38.000Z","msg":"由美國國家航空暨太空總署（NASA）開發的「毅力號」探測車，於上月18日成功登陸火星，為人類太空探索跨進一步，而「毅力號」的女指揮官Diana Trujillo亦成為焦點。Diana在17歲隻身到美國，由不懂英文、半工讀做清潔工，到成為NASA毅力號指揮官，她的奮鬥故事激勵人心。<br />\n<br />\n僅帶300美元到美國做清潔工<br />\n據美國哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）報道，現年41歲的Diana Trujillo來自哥倫比亞，父母在她12歲離異，她自此在單親家庭成長，直至17歲時決定獨自到美國，身上僅帶著300美元（約2,300港元）。當時她不懂英文，找了一份清潔工作，半工讀在佛羅里達大學（University of Florida）完成學業。<br />\n<br />\nDiana指早年的移民經歷，令她凡事盡力而為，不會輕言否定自己，尤其自己來自一個機會有限的國家，去到美國可說處處都是機遇。她一直都以積極的態度面對前路︰<br />\n&quot;我不會說，無法相信我要當清潔工或晚上工作，而是想著很高興我有一份工作，可以買食物，而且有房子讓我睡覺。過去每一刻都很重要，也造就今天的我。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n加入NASA向家人證明能力<br />\n她憶述在佛羅里達大學選科時，根本不知道自己想讀甚麼，但她被雜誌上的女太空人圖片吸引，於是確定路向主修航空航天工程，向太空夢進發。她更留意到航天業缺乏懂西班牙文的人才，而她具備這方面優勢。<br />\n<br />\n在大學四年級時，她申請了NASA Academy培訓計劃，成為第一位加入計劃的西班牙裔女性，並在2007年正式獲NASA聘請，現在是噴射推進實驗室的一員。她不諱言加入NASA的部分原因是，想向家人尤其是男性親友證明，女性也很有價值。<br />\n<br />\n兩孩之母身教凡事盡所能<br />\n當年17歲的少女現在已是兩孩之母，也是從事科學工作中為數不多的拉丁裔之一。Diana有感一路走來太不可思議，不時反問自己為何能走到這一步。當擔起「毅力號」指揮官時，她代表的不僅僅是自己。<br />\n&quot;我知道我不會一個人走，我做的每一件事都代表著國家，必須每次都盡我所能。&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2890000/2893469/NASA_thumb_20210305_E_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2890000%2F2893469%2FNASA_thumb_20210305_E_1024.jpg&h=39597b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2890000/2893469/09_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2890000%2F2893469%2F09_1024.jpg&h=90c43f7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T21:14:47.000Z","msg":"香港人要準備幾千萬先會走難........"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:10:35.000Z","msg":"反差大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個帶住幾舊就衝出去實現夢想<br />\n一個帶住幾千萬都唔情願咁郁去走難"},{"pid":"ceb22559f159ec8e17b8c4f0db8cb7435db75385","tid":2434871,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:16:22.000Z","msg":"唔知佢當年係用咩身分入境美國呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e2c972f4932cbe477027e9ebbe3d61e10064d9","tid":2434871,"uid":17443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:18:29.000Z","msg":"美國夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780e982242eb27c227b53d5090f6f4c3ae9e76ce","tid":2434871,"uid":325878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:20:53.000Z","msg":"佢本人已經係毅力號，NASA係唔係用佢個人經歷來命名<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 佢都幾靚女，佩服"},{"pid":"f974a754b7096a0a2a13abdb61bfafe1c57f9daa","tid":2434871,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"3f5157ff4b6cee811a10b321eafb91d6e22b0a48","tid":2434871,"uid":26770,"like":5